Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.302 --> 00:00:05.338
WELCOME, LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
TO "THE LATE SHOW."

00:00:05.371 --> 00:00:09.742
I'M YOUR HOST STEPHEN COLBERT.

00:00:09.775 --> 00:00:14.881
( CHEERS AND APPLAUSE )
I WANT TO START OUT TONIGHT BY

00:00:14.914 --> 00:00:17.316
SAYING OUR THOUGHTS ARE WITH
YOU, CALIFORNIA.

