THE GOLDEN STATE IS BEING
RAVAGED BY THREE DEADLY

00:00:21.887 --> 00:00:24.390
WILDFIRES IN MALIBU AND NORTHERN
CALIFORNIA.

00:00:24.423 --> 00:00:26.993
THERE'S BEEN TRAGIC LOSS OF LIFE
AND UNPRECEDENTED LOSS OF

00:00:27.026 --> 00:00:29.829
PROPERTY.

00:00:29.862 --> 00:00:33.332
WE CERTAINLY HOPE EVERYBODY
THERE STAYS SAFE, INCLUDING AND

00:00:33.365 --> 00:00:38.071
ESPECIALLY THE FIREFIGHTERS
FIGHTING THIS ON THE FRONT LINE.

00:00:38.104 --> 00:00:39.338
AT A TIME LIKE THIS, IT'S HARD
TO KNOW THE RIGHT THING TO SAY.

00:00:39.371 --> 00:00:40.706
BUT FOR THE WRONG THING TO SAY,
LET'S CHECK THE PRESIDENT'S

00:00:40.739 --> 00:00:42.542
TWITTER FEED.

00:00:42.575 --> 00:00:44.544
( LAUGHTER )
&gt;&gt; STEPHEN (AS TRUMP): "THERE IS

00:00:44.577 --> 00:00:48.681
NO REASON FOR THESE MASSIVE,
DEADLY, AND COSTLY FOREST FIRES

00:00:48.714 --> 00:00:53.553
IN CALIFORNIA EXCEPT THAT FOREST
MANAGEMENT IS SO POOR.

00:00:53.586 --> 00:00:57.223
BILLIONS OF DOLLARS ARE GIVEN
EACH YEAR, WITH SO MANY LIVES

00:00:57.256 --> 00:01:01.761
LOST, ALL BECAUSE OF GROSS
MISMANAGEMENT OF THE FORESTS.

00:01:01.794 --> 00:01:12.138
REMEDY NOW, OR NO MORE FED
PAYMENTS!"

00:01:12.171 --> 00:01:14.407
BOO-BOO
( BOOING )

00:01:14.440 --> 00:01:18.945
&gt;&gt; Stephen: I THINK THAT'S
CALLED BLAMING THE VICTIM.

00:01:18.978 --> 00:01:20.213
