TRUMP THERE TO SAVE ME.

00:01:20.246 --> 00:01:21.347
(AS TRUMP): "ARE YOU CHOKING?

00:01:21.381 --> 00:01:23.749
THERE'S NO REASON FOR THIS
MASSIVE LOSS OF OXYGEN, EXCEPT

00:01:23.782 --> 00:01:26.853
