00:01:34.193 --> 00:01:37.063
TO CALIFORNIA'S FREQUENT
WILDFIRES.

00:01:37.096 --> 00:01:40.066
(AS TRUMP): "WITH PROPER FOREST
MANAGEMENT, WE CAN STOP THE

00:01:40.099 --> 00:01:43.769
DEVASTATION CONSTANTLY GOING ON
IN CALIFORNIA!

00:01:43.802 --> 00:01:48.207
GET SMART!"
"GOT TO BE SMART.

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:54.914
