PLANTING TREES MADE OF WOOD.

00:01:54.947 --> 00:01:56.883
( LAUGHTER )
( PIANO RIFF )

00:01:56.916 --> 00:01:58.217
ROOKIE MISTAKE.

00:01:58.250 --> 00:01:59.785
I WILL REPLACE THEM WITH TREES
MADE OUT OF BEAUTIFUL AMERICAN

00:01:59.818 --> 00:02:01.754
STEEL."

