EASILY THE MOST FLAMMABLE

00:02:07.560 --> 00:02:09.695
PRESIDENT IN U.S. HISTORY.

00:02:09.728 --> 00:02:13.766
( LAUGHTER )
( CHEERS AND APPLAUSE )

00:02:13.799 --> 00:02:15.535
